### 1. 登录并拿到 Token (REST Client 插件会自动帮你把返回的 token 存到变量里)
# @name loginRequest
POST http://127.0.0.1:48789/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "change_me"
}

###

### 2. 随便请求一个受保护的业务接口 (直接引用上面的变量)
@authToken = {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

GET http://127.0.0.1:48789/api/some_protected_route
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}